# Documentation — durable content only

`docs/` describes **current** Orchi behavior.

## Do not add to `docs/`

- Roadmaps / Phase 0–N plans / “done in tree” trackers
- Goals / Non-goals / Success criteria for unfinished work
- “Optional later” feature dumps or agent scratch notes

Those belong in the PR or issue. Prefer one short durable guide over multiple overlapping plan docs.

